image_analysis.description: A photograph of a kitchen interior. The kitchen features white cabinetry, a light-colored countertop, and stainless steel appliances. Visible appliances include a Frigidaire refrigerator, a Frigidaire dishwasher, a white microwave, a toaster, and a silver electric kettle. A sink with a tall faucet is on the left, with soap bottles nearby. A roll of paper towels is on the counter. There is a window above the sink. The floor appears to be a light-colored tile.
image_analysis.layout: The image shows a corner of a kitchen with upper and lower cabinets, a dishwasher, and a refrigerator framing the right side.

notes: The text 'FRIGIDAIRE' appears on both the refrigerator and the dishwasher as brand labels. The code 'EFTA00000302' is a Bates stamp or document identifier added to the bottom right of the image.
